Method Detail

main

public static void main(java.lang.String[] args)
Launches a browser window. If a browser instance is found to already exist, the new browser window is opened in the running application.

Note: To run without an "ext" directory (e.g. from the project source code in Eclipse) you need to set up the "ext.dirs" and/or "ext.files" properties.
